cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.SY

This paper is primarily focused on reinforcement learning and metalearning, which are both subfields of machine learning. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) is the most likely category. The paper also deals with robotics and motor control, which suggests that it could be categorized under cs.RO (Robotics). Additionally, the paper involves computer vision, as it uses mazes as a testing environment, which could place it under cs.CV (Computer Vision). Finally, the paper deals with control systems, which could place it under cs.SY (Systems and Control).
